    requests to blkif. This change reduces the contention on the list of
    available requests.
    
    Signed-off-by: Roger Pau Monné <roger.pau@citrix.com>
    Cc: Konrad Rzeszutek Wilk <konrad.wilk@oracle.com>
    Cc: xen-devel@lists.xen.org
